[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_0",
    "text": "笔记十五 中国的地理差异",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.34681543468154347,
      0.17391304347826086,
      0.6443514644351465,
      0.1963109354413702
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_1",
    "text": "四大地理区域的划分",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.11157601115760112,
      0.23715415019762845,
      0.3272896327289633,
      0.25889328063241107
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_2",
    "text": "1、不同的地理区域",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12366341236634124,
      0.269433465085639,
      0.32264063226406325,
      0.28919631093544135
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_3",
    "text": "地理区域不仅可以划分为多种类型(自然区域、经济区域、行政区域)，而目同 一类型的区域，还可以划分为不同天度或不同级别的区域(如：行政区域：省.县乡；再 如：温度带：热带、亚热带.温带(暖温带.中温带、寒温带))。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10227801022780102,
      0.29907773386034253,
      0.9381682938168294,
      0.38603425559947296
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_4",
    "text": "2.我国的四大地理区域",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11436541143654114,
      0.42555994729907776,
      0.36448163644816367,
      0.44664031620553357
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_5",
    "text": "(1)划分依据：各地的地理位置.自然和人文地理特点的不同。 (2)四大地理区域：北方地区.南方地区、青藏地区，西北地区.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15527661552766156,
      0.4552042160737813,
      0.7726638772663877,
      0.5079051383399209
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_6",
    "text": "(3)四大地理区或的分界线：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1608554160855416,
      0.5184453227931489,
      0.4388656438865644,
      0.538866930171278
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_7",
    "text": "北方地区与南方地区分界线是秦岭—准河一线，主导因素是气温和降水。 北方地区与西北地区分界线是400毫米年等降水量线，主导因素是夏季风的影响。 青藏地区与西北地区分界线是青藏高原边界 主导因素是地势和地形 青藏地区与南方地区分界线是青截高原边界",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18317061831706183,
      0.5454545454545454,
      0.9521152952115295,
      0.66600790513834
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_8",
    "text": "3.秦岭——准河一线代表的地表意义：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11715481171548117,
      0.7048748353096179,
      0.5011622501162251,
      0.7272727272727273
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77_9",
    "text": "(1)1目D℃等温线经过的地区 (2)亚热带与暖温带的分界线 (3)300毫米等降水量线经过的地区 (4)湿润地区与半湿润地区的分界线 (5)旱地农业与水国农业的分界线 (6)亚热带季风气候与温带季风气候的分界线.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16457461645746166,
      0.7371541501976284,
      0.4686192468619247,
      0.7582345191040843
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_77",
    "order": 10
